     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>In memoriam Perkinsi.</head>
   <l>Is Perkins gone, that whilome was a Lamp,</l>
   <l>A Cantabrigian Phôspher shining farre?</l>
   <l>Gon, gon indeed. And yet his deeds remain</l>
   <l>As monuments of such a writers worth.</l>
   <l>Hei-papist snarle, cōtend his works to dim,</l>
   <l>Thou bites &amp; blots thy wretched selfe, not him.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>He. Clapham.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
